Component.description:
Audio component that can be attached to an entity.
This component will play audio spatially from the entity.\n
@param file The Uri String of the audio file to be used\n
@param volume The volume of the audio to be played, default is 1.0f\n
@property audio The Uri String of the audio file to be used\n
@property volume The volume of the audio to be played, default is 1.0f
